data.text:
HIGH SCHOOL

Earned first-team all-state, first-team all-region, first-team all-district and academic all-district honors in 2022... earned second-team all-state, second-team all-region and academic all-district honors in 2021... won the individual title at the district championships in 2021... was named the most outstanding golfer of the year in 2021 and 2020... earned academic all-district honors in 2020... led her team to a state, regional and district championship in 2022... led her team to a district championship in 2021... helped her team to a second-place finish at regionals in 2021... helped her team to a fifth-place finish at the state championships in 2021... competed in The US Kids Golf, STPGA, TJGT, Legends Junior and AJGA Tours... played at the following tournaments: 2019 The Optimist, 2020 Rolex Girls Junior Championship, 2021 Notah Begay III Jr. Golf National Championship, 2021 & 2022 The Kathy Whitworth Girls Invitational, 2022 The Bubba, 2022 The Northern Junior... played in over 300 tournaments with 95 first-place wins... was a six-time U.S. Kids Golf Local Tour Champion, a 2018 Srixon Prestige Tour Champion, a two-time TJGT Elite Series Champion, a 2020 TJGT All-Tour Team member, a Legends Junior Tour Champion, a two-time top-5 AJGA finisher and a four-time top-10 AJGA finisher... helped her team win the 2017 Texas Mexico Cup and the 2018 Texas Junior Cup... also helped her team win the 2020, 2021 and 2022 Greenwood Cup and the 2021 and 2022 AJGA Texas Cup.

PERSONAL

Daughter of Tony and Eydie Webster... majoring in business.
